Objects.Name: card ace wands
Objects.ExtraDescription: Selfishness may spoil the beginning.

Objects.Name: card ace cups
Objects.ExtraDescription: Egotism and selfishness will interfere with new beginnings.

Objects.Name: card ace swords
Objects.ExtraDescription: A good beginning may have a destructive ending.

Objects.Name: card ace pentacles
Objects.ExtraDescription: Beware of greed or miserliness.

Objects.Name: card two wands
Objects.ExtraDescription: Be patient, a watched pot never boils.

Objects.Name: card two cups
Objects.ExtraDescription: There are difficulties in a new romance or friendship.

Objects.Name: card two swords
Objects.ExtraDescription: A decision is being made but it may be the wrong one.

Objects.Name: card two pentacles
Objects.ExtraDescription: Doing too much at one time can lead to problems.

Objects.Name: card three wands
Objects.ExtraDescription: Arrogance may lead to trying to do too much at one time.

Objects.Name: card three cups
Objects.ExtraDescription: Gossip will interfere with your pleasures.

Objects.Name: card three swords
Objects.ExtraDescription: Romance may be confusing right now.

Objects.Name: card three pentacles
Objects.ExtraDescription: Laziness will lead to mediocrity.

Objects.Name: card four wands
Objects.ExtraDescription: Appreciate the good things that are happening in your life.

Objects.Name: card four cups
Objects.ExtraDescription: New goals are in sight.

Objects.Name: card four swords
Objects.ExtraDescription: After a rest comes renewed activity.

Objects.Name: card four pentacles
Objects.ExtraDescription: Financial problems could be ahead if you aren't careful.

Objects.Name: card five wands
Objects.ExtraDescription: Competition may be enjoyable.

Objects.Name: card five cups
Objects.ExtraDescription: Hope and courage will lead you through difficulties.

Objects.Name: card five swords
Objects.ExtraDescription: A feeling of unfairness may interfere with the pleasure of winning.

Objects.Name: card five pentacles
Objects.ExtraDescription: Charity will be good for your emotional health.

Objects.Name: card six wands
Objects.ExtraDescription: Good news may be on the way, but delayed.

Objects.Name: card six cups
Objects.ExtraDescription: Its time to let the past go and live in the present.

Objects.Name: card six swords
Objects.ExtraDescription: You cannot run away from present problems.

Objects.Name: card six pentacles
Objects.ExtraDescription: Beware of gifts given that may be bribes.

Objects.Name: card seven wands
Objects.ExtraDescription: Beware of indecision and people taking advantage of you.

Objects.Name: card seven cups
Objects.ExtraDescription: Focusing on the matter with determination will lead to success.

Objects.Name: card seven swords
Objects.ExtraDescription: Listen to good advice.

Objects.Name: card seven pentacles
Objects.ExtraDescription: This matter may not be worth the work you put into it.

Objects.Name: card eight wands
Objects.ExtraDescription: Jealousy may lead to quarrels.

Objects.Name: card eight cups
Objects.ExtraDescription: Enjoyment and romance may be ahead.

Objects.Name: card eight swords
Objects.ExtraDescription: Problems will soon release their hold on you.

Objects.Name: card eight pentacles
Objects.ExtraDescription: Be careful of how you use your skills.

Objects.Name: card nine wands
Objects.ExtraDescription: You'd better start thinking ahead because you aren't ready for what liesahead of you.

Objects.Name: card nine cups
Objects.ExtraDescription: You aren't happy with what you have.

Objects.Name: card nine swords
Objects.ExtraDescription: Things will get better over time.

Objects.Name: card nine pentacles
Objects.ExtraDescription: Be careful of what you have, you may be losing something.

Objects.Name: card ten wands
Objects.ExtraDescription: Try to work out the reasons that things are done.  Be wary of meansjustifying bad ends.

Objects.Name: card ten cups
Objects.ExtraDescription: There may be family difficulties here.

Objects.Name: card ten swords
Objects.ExtraDescription: This may be a good time to fight for what you believe in.

Objects.Name: card ten pentacles
Objects.ExtraDescription: This is not a good time to take risks.

Objects.Name: card Page Wands
Objects.ExtraDescription: The person involved is unstable and may be a disappointment.

Objects.Name: card Page Cups
Objects.ExtraDescription: The person involved is selfish and may use others.

Objects.Name: card Page Swords
Objects.ExtraDescription: The person involved is frivolous and should not be trusted.

Objects.Name: card Page Pentacles
Objects.ExtraDescription: The person involved has a rebellious nature.

Objects.Name: card Knight Wands
Objects.ExtraDescription: The person involved can be narrow-minded and disruptive.

Objects.Name: card Knight Cups
Objects.ExtraDescription: The person involved may lie, but not always maliciously.

Objects.Name: card Knight Swords
Objects.ExtraDescription: The person involved may be a troublemaker and a bully.

Objects.Name: card Knight Pentacles
Objects.ExtraDescription: The person involved is irresponsible.

Objects.Name: card Queen Wands
Objects.ExtraDescription: The person involved is honest but domineering.

Objects.Name: card Queen Cups
Objects.ExtraDescription: The person involved is imaginative and helpful.

Objects.Name: card Queen Swords
Objects.ExtraDescription: The person involved is perceptive and has a strong character.

Objects.Name: card Queen Pentacles
Objects.ExtraDescription: The person involved is thoughtful and good at business.

Objects.Name: card King Wands
Objects.ExtraDescription: The person involved is agile and passionate.

Objects.Name: card King Cups
Objects.ExtraDescription: The person involved is calm but powerful.

Objects.Name: card King Swords
Objects.ExtraDescription: The person involved is commanding but overcautious.

Objects.Name: card King Pentacles
Objects.ExtraDescription: The person involved is good at mathematics and finances.

Objects.Name: card 0 Fool
Objects.ExtraDescription: Joys and possibilities may lie ahead if you choose wisely.

Objects.Name: card I Magician
Objects.ExtraDescription: This card shows a person who can turn ideas into reality.

Objects.Name: card II High Priestess
Objects.ExtraDescription: Not all things can or should be understood.  Some things can only be felt.

Objects.Name: card III Empress
Objects.ExtraDescription: This card shows fertility of thought, mind or body.

Objects.Name: card IV Emperor
Objects.ExtraDescription: This card shows leadership qualities, either in yourself or in someone in aposition of authority over you.

Objects.Name: card V Hierophant
Objects.ExtraDescription: This card shows conventionality and conformity.  You are swayed by a need forsocial approval.

Objects.Name: card VI Lovers
Objects.ExtraDescription: A choice is offered, possibly between temptation and romance.

Objects.Name: card VII Chariot
Objects.ExtraDescription: Hard work leads to success.

Objects.Name: card VIII Strength
Objects.ExtraDescription: Love has triumphed over hate, consideration over obstinence.

Objects.Name: card IX Hermit
Objects.ExtraDescription: You are open minded enough to accept the wisdom of others.

Objects.Name: card X Wheel Fortune
Objects.ExtraDescription: Fortune has ups and downs, and right now your luck is up.  Build on it.

Objects.Name: card XI Justice
Objects.ExtraDescription: The judgment is fair and well balanced.

Objects.Name: card XII Hanged
Objects.ExtraDescription: This would be a good time to concentrate on the spiritual side of life.

Objects.Name: card XIII Death
Objects.ExtraDescription: This card does not suggest a person's death but the rebirth and renewal of amatter.

Objects.Name: card XIV Temperance
Objects.ExtraDescription: This indicates a successful combination of some sort.

Objects.Name: card XV Devil
Objects.ExtraDescription: There is a temptation to choose the material over the spiritual.  Watch allchoices carefully.

Objects.Name: card XVI Tower
Objects.ExtraDescription: Ambition is overthrown, leaving room for new ideas.

Objects.Name: card XVII Star
Objects.ExtraDescription: Inspiration will lead to good things.

Objects.Name: card XVIII Moon
Objects.ExtraDescription: Beware of deception, leading to unforeseen perils.

Objects.Name: card XIX Sun
Objects.ExtraDescription: Achievements in some area are indicated.

Objects.Name: card XX Judgement
Objects.ExtraDescription: A sense of renewal leads to a new outlook.

Objects.Name: card XXI World
Objects.ExtraDescription: Triumph and fulfillment in the matter in question.

Objects.Name: glass tarot large milk
Objects.Description: A large etched glass waits to be used.
Objects.ExtraDescription: The large glass, made out of thick, strong glass, has something etched intoone side.

Objects.Name: urn milk
Objects.Description: A milk urn waits here, hospitably.
Objects.ExtraDescription: A tall, clear urn stands here, filled with white foamy liquid.  A protrudingtap allows you to fill your glass with nice, cold milk.

Objects.Name: bokolyitarot breadtarot
Objects.Description: A piece of bokolyi sits here, waiting to be eaten.
Objects.ExtraDescription: It's a piece of flatbread, warm and comforting.  It has a delicious odor thatseems homelike.

Objects.Name: quill pen
Objects.Description: A quill pen lies here with ink on the nib.
